'''''Xroi''''' was a group of 2 [[BFF-1 bulk freighter/Legends|BFF-1 bulk freighters]] used by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]. The two freighters were part of a convoy including 3 [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]] called ''[[Qiluiy]]'' in the [[Mennaalii system]] which came under attack by [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] aboard the frigate [[Scorpion (EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate)|''Scorpion'']]. However the pirate attack was driven off by Rebel [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wings]], [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|Y-wings]], and [[RZ-1 A-wing interceptor/Legends|A-wings]].

